Project Plan

1. Discuss Requirements
2. Create Project Plan
3. Design Program Algorithnm
4. Write Code Using Python 
5. Debug Code
6. Test Program
7. Present Working Program

Program Requirements

1. Program must backup both files and directories
2. The program must run both manually and as a scheduled task
3. The program must accept a CLI indicating the job
4. Backup job details must be defined in backupcgf.py
5. The program must gracefully handle incorrect or missing input
6. The program must log all jobs to backup.log
7. The program must send an email if the backup fails
8. Program must comply with Coding Standards provided
9. Source files and directories must be copied to the destination directory
10. Explanatory comments are used throughout the code